text: Swetnam is a surname. People with the name include: * Huw Swetnam, British slalom canoeist * Joseph Swetnam (died 1621), English pamphleteer and fencing master * Thomas W. Swetnam (born 1955), American dendrochronologist == See also == * Swetnam the Woman-Hater, a Jacobean era stage play
title: Swetnam
